---
interface Props {}
---

<section id="shop-impact" class="py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 text-center lg:max-w-[960px]" data-animate="fade-up">
    <h2 class="font-heading text-[clamp(28px,4vw,36px)] font-medium leading-tight text-text-heading">
      Every Purchase Makes an Impact
    </h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-[700px] font-body text-base leading-relaxed text-text-body">
      When you shop with Jewmanity, you're not just getting quality merchandise—you're directly funding healing retreats, peer support groups, and ongoing care for individuals and families in our community. Your purchase creates lasting change and supports those on their healing journey.
    </p>

    <div class="mx-auto mt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-8 sm:flex-row sm:gap-16">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
        <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12Z" />
        </svg>
        <span class="font-body text-sm font-medium text-text-heading">Healing Retreats</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
        <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19.128a9.38 9.38 0 0 0 2.625.372 9.337 9.337 0 0 0 4.121-.952 4.125 4.125 0 0 0-7.533-2.493M15 19.128v-.003c0-1.113-.285-2.16-.786-3.07M15 19.128v.106A12.318 12.318 0 0 1 8.624 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0 1 11.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 1 1-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 0 1 6.75 0Zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 1 1-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 0 1 5.25 0Z" />
